 The following datasets are available:                <UL><li> TP53 <strong>somatic mutations</strong> in sporadic cancers</li>	                <li> TP53 <strong>germline mutation</strong><b> </b>in familial cancers</li>                <li> Common TP53 <strong>polymorphisms</strong> identified in human populations</li>                <li> <strong>Functional and structural properties</strong> of P53 mutant proteins</li>                <li> TP53 gene status in human <strong>cell-lines</strong></li>                <li> <strong>Mouse-models</strong> with engineered TP53</li>                </UL>						See detailed information on database contents in the <a href="Help.html">user's guide</a>.<br>							<br>						</a>				<script type="text/javascript">databaseref1()</script>	<BR>				<div class="separatorblue">IARC TP53 DATABASE Recent News</div> 								<script type="text/javascript">news1()</script>				See Previous <A HREF="p53news.html">News</A><BR>						<BR>					</div>           </td>         </tr>     </table>	 <BR>	<div align="left"><script type="text/javascript">bottom1()</script></div>  </body></html>